sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Analyst
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Service
    participant Agent as AI Agent (Claude)
    participant Tools as Agent Tools
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Types message in chat interface
    FE->>API: POST /chat {session_id, message}
    API->>DB: Load conversation history for session
    DB-->>API: Prior messages
    API->>Agent: Send message + history + system prompt + tool definitions

    loop Agent reasoning (multi-step tool use)
        Agent->>Agent: Reason about next action

        alt Needs data — use a tool
            Agent->>Tools: Call tool (e.g. search_knowledge, get_error_summary)
            Tools->>DB: Query or write
            DB-->>Tools: Result
            Tools-->>Agent: Tool result
        else Ready to respond
            Agent->>Agent: Compose final response
        end
    end

    Agent->>DB: Save user message + assistant response to conversation_messages
    opt Agent extracts business knowledge from the conversation
        Agent->>DB: Write knowledge_entry + generate embedding (pgvector)
    end

    Agent-->>API: Response text
    API-->>FE: {response, session_id}
    FE-->>U: Display agent response in chat
